-- Australia Will Play Four Fast Bowlers in 3rd Ashes Cricket Test in Perth
-- B y   D a n   B a y n e s
-- 2010-12-16T01:46:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-16/australia-will-play-four-fast-bowlers-in-3rd-ashes-cricket-test-in-perth.html
Australia will go into the third
Ashes cricket Test against England with a four-man pace attack
of Mitchell Johnson, Peter Siddle, Ryan Harris and Ben
Hilfenhaus.  Specialist spin bowler Michael Beer was left out of the
final 11 and will be the 12th man for the match at the WACA,
Cricket Australia said. The match starts at 10:30 a.m. local
time.  AUSTRALIA: Shane Watson, Phillip Hughes, Ricky Ponting
(captain), Michael Clarke, Michael Hussey, Steven Smith, Brad
Haddin, Mitchell Johnson, Peter Siddle, Ryan Harris, Ben
Hilfenhaus.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Baynes at 
 dbaynes@bloomberg.net  